    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E92 M3 featuring the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This power plant utilizes eight individual throttle bodies to produce 414 hp, reaching its peak at a stratospheric 8,300 RPM. The drivetrain is anchored by a traditional 6-speed manual transmission and the M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring precise torque distribution across the rear axle. The chassis retains its structural integrity, benefiting from the factory carbon fiber roof which lowers the center of gravity. Recent service includes rod bearing replacement and new throttle actuators, mitigating common S65 failure points. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the Electronic Damper Control (EDC) and bushings remain tight, providing the communicative feedback and lateral stability expected of the M-division\u2019s engineering.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 2
    },
